{"type":"text","timestamp":1779249982864,"sessionID":"ses_1bc8c0a70ffemYD3KuZZ4coPT1","part":{"id":"prt_e438ffab50016nfiWdNo1Moxat","messageID":"msg_e438feee5001ijp3l4nDPd0MsN","sessionID":"ses_1bc8c0a70ffemYD3KuZZ4coPT1","type":"text","text":"Implementation complete. Here's a summary:\n\n**Properties Module — 9 endpoints, 71 targeted tests, `npx tsc --noEmit` clean**\n\n### Files Created (4)\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `dtos/create-property.dto.ts` | CreatePropertyDto + AddressDto with full validation |\n| `dtos/update-property.dto.ts` | UpdatePropertyDto (all fields optional) |\n| `dtos/reorder-photos.dto.ts` | ReorderPhotosDto (UUID array) |\n| `property-photo.repository.ts` | PropertyPhotoRepository extending BaseRepository |\n\n### Files Modified (4)\n| File | Key Changes |\n|------|-------------|\n| `property.repository.ts` | Fixed price range bug (min+max overwrote each other), added state/oldest filters, eager-loaded amenities |\n| `property.service.ts` | Address nest/flatten, photo management (upload/delete/primary/reorder), `isFavorited` check, syncAmenities |\n| `property.controller.ts` | Typed DTOs, 4 new photo endpoints, FilesInterceptor for multipart, `@CurrentUser()` for isFavorited |\n| `property.module.ts` | Added Favorite entity import, PropertyPhotoRepository provider |\n\n### Key Design Decisions\n- **Address**: flat columns in DB → nested `{ street, city, state, zipCode, latitude, longitude }` in API\n- **isFavorited**: always `false` for unauthenticated; checks `Favorite` table via direct TypeORM injection (no FavoriteModule dependency)\n- **Photo upload**: `FilesInterceptor('files', 10)` with `memoryStorage()`; first photo auto-primary\n- **No base class override**: `getPropertyDetail()` as custom method instead of overriding `findByIdOrFail`\n\nReport written to `.claude-project/nestfind/status/BACKEND_IMPLEMENT_properties.md`","time":{"start":1779249969845,"end":1779249982861}}}
